 FCT Minister, Malam Muhammad Musa Bello. Photo: FACEBOOK  Bello disclosure this yesterday at a news conference in Abuja, explaining that while boarding schools resume on Sunday, day schools would resume on Monday, October 12. He said the decision to re-open schools was probably one of the most painstaking decisions that the FCT Administration had to take a team. “In opening of schools, we have to be very careful and conscious of the need to ensure that all our efforts during the last few months are not in vain,” he said.  To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .